window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Joining us in the Audible Studios to talk about his latest thriller,<i> Kill for Me</i>,<i> </i>is British author Tom Wood.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>After publishing his first book, <i>The Hunter</i>, in 2010, Tom Wood has gone on to write seven more titles within his Victor the Assassin series, which features his cold assassin antihero, Victor. He has now published the exciting eighth installment, <i>Kill for Me</i>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Tom wood talks to us about his latest book, his infamous antihero and the supporting characters he loves to write.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"; 
